$interpreted: Slums Man: Get out! You will not tear it down!
Slums Woman: Give me back my job!
Simon: Fellow residents, today's teardown is for the prosperity of the future. Please don't stand in our way.
Simon: We will finish as soon as possible and give everyone a better life!
Nigel: Everybody, please calm down!
Nigel: Cin, why are you here?
Slums Man: Nigel, don't be fooled by these guys!
Slums Woman: The blueprint mentioned nothing about tearing down this area, tell them to get out!
Slums Man: Get Out! Get Out! Get Out!
Hyacinthus: They're using force!
Slums Woman: Don't let them get away!
Nigel: Calm down, don't get so agitated~
Lucky: Hmph! Pesky slumdogs!
Simon: Escort Mr. Spencer out of here!
Slums Man: Charge! GET' EM!!
Nigel: Stop, don't do this!
Slums Woman: There's a fire!!
Nigel: Everybody, please stop! STOP IT!
Nigel: Why hasn't Eve shown up...
Jim: Arggghhhh!!!
Nigel: How are you feeling? Are you ok?
Jim: I... c-cold, so cold...everything...hurts...give... gimme...that powder...the pain...
Nigel: Where did you get this powder?
Jim: Brother...I'm sorry...please...just another hit...just one...
Nigel: This has ruined you. Tell me where you got it!
Jim: I-I don't know either...it was just one night at the bar...
Nigel: Take care of the people here for me. I'll be right back.
Hyacinthus: Understood.
